# The repo-root .gitignore ignores all `dist/` directories. Our dist/ is not a
# build artifact — it's a committed placeholder required by tauri.conf.json's
# frontendDist ("../dist") so `tauri build` can package. Un-ignore it here.
!dist/
!dist/index.html

# Node deps for the Tauri CLI are reinstalled via `npm install`.
node_modules/
